retrieve time series dataset from USA Facts

Source: R/usa_facts_data.R
usa_facts_data.Rd

This always does a web call. The assumption here is that the user is online and that github is up and that URLs are stable.

usa_facts_data()

Value

an object of class s2p_long_df that inherits from tbl_df

Note

Uses https://usafacts.org/visualizations/coronavirus-covid-19-spread-map/ as data source, then modifies column names and munges to long form table.

See also

jhu_data()

Other data-import: jhu_data()
